# Project Structure Conventions

## Service Naming
- Format: `{domain}-{type}` (e.g., `trade-rpc`, `promotion-api`, `user-rpc`)
- API services: `cmd/api/{domain}-api/`
- RPC services: `cmd/rpc/{domain}-rpc/`
- Service implementations: `service/{domain}/rpc/`

## Directory Structure
```
cmd/
  api/          # HTTP API services (BFF layer)
  rpc/          # gRPC services (business logic layer)
service/        # Domain services implementation
  {domain}/
    rpc/        # RPC service implementation
common/         # Shared utilities
  middleware/   # Common middleware
  mq/          # Message queue utilities
  snowflake/   # ID generation
doc/           # Documentation
  design/      # Architecture design docs
  coding-standards/  # Coding standards
```
